annel state information (CSI) update rate requirement may increase by 7\ntimes when compared to an 8-antenna system, whilst the power control update\nrate could be decreased by at least 5 times relative to a single antenna\nsystem.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 Jan 2017 20:33:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 28 Feb 2017 20:29:18 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 20 May 2017 01:18:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-05-23"}
