ents) in\nan otherwise random impact record can thus give rise to false periodicity peaks\nin a CSA. There is currently no evidence for periodicity in the impact record.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 31 Jan 2017 09:12:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-01"}
